README
=======

++ Description
	- This is a simple script that extracts data from a database after a specified interval, creates a csv file of the data and sends an email with the file as an attachment.
	- Utilises inmemory Db and supervisor
	- Check out the sample config file
	- Developed for linux
	- Change necessary configs and directories to match your environment
	
++ Dependencies
	- Python 2.7
	- pydblite
	- run script via supervisor

++ Others

	full path - /opt/scripts/stats_gen/stats_generator.py

	#Supervisor config
	[program:stats_gen]
	directory=/opt/scripts/stats_gen/
	command=python /opt/scripts/stats_gen/stats_generator.py
	autostart=true
	startsecs=0
	autorestart=false
	redirect_stderr=true